    General Stores in Nahur, Mumbai

    (1176 Ratings & Reviews) 4.2 Average Ratings

    General Stores in Nahur, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. In certain metros and cities, a general store can also be a part of a pharmacy or medicine shop. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. The vast list of general store items does not limit to food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Depending on the location of the store  whether in a rural village or an urban metropolis  the stock keeping units or pack sizes of the packaged goods may differ. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Nahur, Mumbai.
